if suddenly the entire system was down, for trobleshooting the issue is :
- Check every vm , running or shutdown
- Check logging on OS 
- Check Disk Of VM 
- Check Network 
- Check Host Of VM Utilitas



for preventive issue system sudenly down , we must design infrasturcture high availabity 
- Deploy Kubernetes Cluster With Multi DC / Region
- or we must setup enviroment DC and DRC with standby mode (active - passive) 
- Setup Tools Utitlas Monitoring like Grafana And Promethues etc